org.openpsa.contacts Changelog
                   ------------------------------
Legend:
- All items marked with "!" represent a major API-Change that is
  not guaranteed to be backwards compatible to previous versions
  which might even break existing functionality.
- All items marked with "+" represent completely new features.


2010-06-01 gudd
  - removed invoice-information from schema oforganization 
    (new table in o.o.invoices)
    
2006-11-27 bergie
  + Fixed account creation

2006-11-03 rambo
  + added link to invoices component (if in use) from group.
  - version bump

2006-10-31 bergie
  + Added initial person delete support. For now this doesn't do anything
    about dependencies

2006-10-30 bergie
  ! Ported contact display and editing to datamanager2
  + Added support for probing semantic web information from company and
    person URLs. Currently only geographical position is used
  + Added support for using different editing fields for employees of "My
    company" than of other contacts

2006-10-17 rambo
  - localized plaintext password prompt
  - version bump

2006-10-16 rambo
  + Added possibility to store person password as plaintext
  - changed crypt routines so that we never have nonprintable characters
    in the hashed password (otherwise replication breaks)
  - version bump

2006-10-09 rambo
  + added global variable to check before loading members array
  - version bump

2006-10-03 rambo
  - added ignore_user_abort()s to duplicate cron handlers

2006-09-04 rambo
  - Finalized cron job to clean dangling duplicate references
  + added the merge persons to navigation when merge is needed

2006-08-31 rambo
  - duplicate merge improvements
  + Cron job to find and mark duplicates daily
  + STUB Cron job to find and remove dangling duplicate marks

2006-08-29 rambo
  + duplicate merge now checks each component (contacts included) for
    a method to merge the duplicates and if present calls it
  + added the method mentioned above to contacts interface class.

2006-08-28 rambo
  - Made duplicate detection slightly better
  + Added an exec method for searching duplicate persons and groups and marking them as such
  + UI for managing duplicates
  + STUB Helper for merging duplicates

2006-08-25 rambo
  - changed default username creation logic (to email sans the domain part)

2006-08-24 rambo
  + added a stub implementation of universalchooser create handler

2006-08-07 bergie
  + Switched organization creation to use correct ACL check

